362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:32:16.000Z","msg":"去年9月22日晚上市民於屯門V city商場外聚集，六旬地盤工其間單獨趨近警方防線指罵警員，被指曾雙手推警署警長，又踢傷制服他的警員。地盤工被控兩項襲警罪，早前審訊時，有作供警員被辯方發現將資料暗中寫於手掌上，但原審裁判官裁定所有警員證人誠實可靠，被告罪成判囚五星期。被告就定罪及刑期提上訴，今於高等法院審理。上訴方質疑兩名警員證供南轅北轍，互相矛盾，裁判官卻照樣接納。惟法官潘敏琦聽罷雙方陳詞後駁回上訴，稍後頒發理由，而保釋中的被告須即時收監。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/SKLLIUQ6HVBCNOAGKDLKCUBMLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FSKLLIUQ6HVBCNOAGKDLKCUBMLM%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxaha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=20d2eb66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FSKLLIUQ6HVBCNOAGKDLKCUBMLM%2F&h=49f9174e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/SKLLIUQ6HVBCNOAGKDLKCUBMLM/</a>"},{"pid":"5c7cf1133d181ddb4972f4023a196bbbe4e2625c","tid":2267396,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f13f888f77669ef92e9bce22c5d271b0388cd58","tid":2267396,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce71164e70ea0931e343e365bcd827a504be3ac3","tid":2267396,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as